{
  "stem": "21482.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Wawel, the castle, the old castle, that's what they had-- was a headquarter for this part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's where Frank--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [BACKGROUND NOISE] I don't remember exactly how long it was before my father came back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think probably it was just a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when of course then Germany declared war on Russia and I guess all the men felt that it would be safe for them to come back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they had to come back because of their families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father and his brothers who were all married, they came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the single brothers remain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had two single brothers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They remained in Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father and my uncles and the neighbors, they had to smuggle themselves back to Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had to swim the Bug River.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not everyone was a good swimmer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father was a very good swimmer, and my father saved a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they started to come back, the men started to come back, I remember I was standing outside of the house one afternoon.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw one of my neighbors come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of my boyfriend's fathers came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just knew in my heart that my father would come back, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father came back the next day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the period of time before my father came back-- and again, I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember there was a Jewish holiday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, as soon as the Germans came in, we couldn't go to the temple anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the synagogues anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't go to schools anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the men in the neighborhood would come to pray in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
